Aaliyah was an unstoppable icon whose groundbreaking R&B music and her film roles continue to inspire us, decades after her demise. Now, MAC cosmetics will give her countless fans a chance to celebrate her music and style using a beauty collection. MAC X Aaliyah collection The limited MAC X Aaliyah beauty collection goes online on June 20th and hits select stores on June 21st. Take a quick look at all the products set to be released. The best part about them is that they were named after some of her top hits. MAC X Aaliyah collection Eyeshadow palette from MAC X Aaliyah collection Lipstick from MAC X Aaliyah collection Lip gloss from MAC X Aaliyah collection Bronzing powder from MAC X Aaliyah collection Lip pencils from MAC X Aaliyah collection